.clif Test Case

function u0:5() -> i128, i64 system_v {
                                block0:
@0001                               v5 = bconst.b1 false
@0001                               brz v5, block3  ; v5 = false
                                    jump block1

                                block1:
@0003                               v12 = iconst.i64 0
@0003                               v13 = uextend.i128 v12  ; v12 = 0
@000a                               jump block5(v13)

                                block3:
@000b                               v21 = iconst.i128 0

                                block5(v23: i128):
@0011                               v29 = iconst.i64 0
@001c                               return v23, v29  ; v29 = 0
}

  • Compile it for riscv64

It compiles
